:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/recurring-task-111x150.png 111w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Add task subject<\/li><li>On the recurring field select repeat interval, you can also select custom interval to fit for your needs.<\/li><li>Save the task<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>How the task will be repeated?<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you set start date 2016-09-27 and set repeat every week the task will be auto created after 7 days from the start date, in this case the task will be auto created on 2016-10-03.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>How will I receive notification when the task will be re-created?<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The task assignees will receive an email and web notification that new task is assigned to them or simply you will be able to notice the new task in the tasks list area.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stop a recurring task<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>First, find your recurring task by applying a filter to the Tasks table as shown below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"418\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks-1024x418.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4246\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks-1024x418.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks-300x122.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks-768x314.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks-1536x627.png 1536w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks-60x24.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks-150x61.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/perfexcrm-recurring-tasks.png 1891w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then edit the task and set the <strong>Repeat Every<\/strong> drop-down field to empty.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"618\" height=\"615\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/stop-recurring-task.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4247\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/stop-recurring-task.png 618w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/stop-recurring-task-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/stop-recurring-task-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/stop-recurring-task-60x60.png 60w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 618px) 100vw, 618px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Notes<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>1. This feature requires CRON Job setup to work properly.<br>2.&nbsp;This feature is added in version 1.2.4<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Recurring tasks is a feature that allows you to create tasks that will repeat on a given period. To create recurring task go to the Tasks menu in the admin area and click on the top left button New task A popup modal will be shown to add new task. Add task subject On the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-857","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-tasks"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/857","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"hr